{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be cozy and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Legal - Your Trusted Advisors</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #8B0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #A0522D; /* Sienna */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #f0f0f0;\n            --background-color: #F5F5DC; /* Beige */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            background-color: #fcfcfc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .section h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact-item {\n            margin: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-item p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Crimson Legal</h1>\n        <p>Your Pillars of Justice, Rooted in Tradition and Excellence.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#services\">Our Services</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#team\">Our Team</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact Us</a></li>\n        </ul>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>About Crimson Legal</h2>\n            <p>Crimson Legal is a distinguished law firm dedicated to providing unparalleled legal counsel with a personal touch. We blend extensive experience with a commitment to integrity and client advocacy, ensuring your legal needs are met with precision and care. Our cozy and approachable atmosphere is designed to make you feel comfortable and confident as we navigate complex legal landscapes together.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <p>We offer a comprehensive range of legal services, tailored to meet the unique needs of each client. Our expertise spans across various practice areas, including:</p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Corporate Law</li>\n                <li>Real Estate Law</li>\n                <li>Estate Planning</li>\n                <li>Family Law</li>\n                <li>Litigation</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>Every case is approached with meticulous attention to detail and a deep understanding of the law.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"team\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>\n            <p>Our team of seasoned legal professionals is passionate about delivering exceptional results. With years of combined experience, we are equipped to handle your most challenging legal matters.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                    <p><strong>Eleanor Vance</strong></p>\n                    <p>Senior Partner</p>\n                    <p><em>Specializing in Corporate Law</em></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                    <p><strong>Arthur Sterling</strong></p>\n                    <p>Partner</p>\n                    <p><em>Expert in Real Estate and Estate Planning</em></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                    <p><strong>Beatrice Croft</strong></p>\n                    <p>Associate Attorney</p>\n                    <p><em>Dedicated to Family Law and Litigation</em></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>We are here to listen and offer guidance. Schedule a consultation to discuss your legal concerns with our dedicated team.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                    <p><strong>Address:</strong></p>\n                    <p>123 Crimson Lane, Suite 400</p>\n                    <p>Redwood City, CA 94063</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                    <p><strong>Phone:</strong></p>\n                    <p>(555) 123-4567</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                    <p><strong>Email:</strong></p>\n                    <p>info@crimsonlegal.com</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <a href=\"mailto:info@crimsonlegal.com\" class=\"btn\">Schedule a Consultation</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Legal. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}